// ### MapServer::ServerMapping ###
//	MoveAble=1  DestServerCode=-1  → this server OWNS this map
//	MoveAble=0  DestServerCode=X   → redirect to server X for this map
//
// STRICTLY NO COMMENTS INSIDE TAGS
-->

